{"tid":1792822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開定先] 今日城市論壇講dq有周庭","createTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T04:57:52.000Z","uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"04410aa8d06a462e7c48d7006d6aaa84ba8d6063","tid":1792822,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"記得去佢地fb投埋票 仲搞唔搞補選<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/551732645018780/posts/1209365719255466/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F551732645018780%2Fposts%2F1209365719255466%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3BvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=a282f879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/551732645018780/posts/1209365719255466/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a4a7770614d60aa5ec7c316ee984456c582eff45","tid":1792822,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"大家星期日有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<br />\n<br />\nPS: 就算唔係金融界的同業，都麻煩like and share，俾多一個人睇到，就多一分機會團結同路人，拜托拜托🙏<br />\n<br />\n#香港金融業職工總會<br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#HKFU<br />\n#收會員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107457800635080%2Fposts%2F159723118741881%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3BvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=7df62429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"f6c7017998fb2d355a8358236f1cfc1cbe4bbb4e","tid":1792822,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:41.000Z","msg":"2019年12月22日《城市論壇》<br />\n主題：<br />\n呈請雖得直 泛民失兩席<br />\nDQ論權力 補選尋共識<br />\n<br />\n台上嘉賓：<br />\n#范國威 立法會前議員<br />\n#周庭 2018年立法會補選（香港島）呈請人<br />\n#陳家珮 2018年立法會補選（香港島）參選人<br />\n#黃成智 2018年立法會補選（新界東）參選人<br />\n<br /